{"tid":1424491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手足今晚真係唔好放火同扔嘢","createTime":"2019-08-06T15:58:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T19:33:48.000Z","uid":40226,"like":68,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"66d5607c88ed44272b0f58d8090fcc6fd3c00931","tid":1424491,"uid":40226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:58:34.000Z","msg":"如果有人咁做<br />\n希望大家有禮貌咁勸佢<br />\n我明大家好嬲好大仇恨<br />\n但請謹記唔好比仇恨所支配<br />\n對家武力已經比我地強<br />\n我地一定要冷靜咁處理好每一步<br />\n我認為到依家係要同佢地鬥耐性<br />\n今晚深水埗係歷史建築<br />\n若果被破壞將會另我地受更大嘅壓力<br />\n班狗會換黑衫已經係事實<br />\n但為防內部分化<br />\n請大家記住有禮理性<br />\n雙方嘗試用理據說服大家"},{"pid":"e0a7f742bc7184ce6c29d72b21d16f556eb2c1c7","tid":1424491,"uid":40226,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"199b0ab8c3625dc7545e6fa85c62310142a2dba4","tid":1424491,"uid":40226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:59:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74541187081f9a0a757af6ec80a00a207c2b5288","tid":1424491,"uid":40226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5edbe394f670a0402c8d9fc86a6221d792c397e0","tid":1424491,"uid":40226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:59:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86769e436d7b924a59bbb45f412e9adce3c5455f","tid":1424491,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"puah"},{"pid":"087967ef57370051eb3a080eb994860748e0ff7e","tid":1424491,"uid":289124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:00:16.000Z","msg":"唔係散左咩？"},{"pid":"7351ce516f7f82391d878770c44a85a1d329cd03","tid":1424491,"uid":82588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT